The paper discusses the development of intrusion detection systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also compares the performance of different machine learning techniques, such as Multivariate Adaptive Regression Splines (MARS), neural networks, and support vector machines, which are commonly used in the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and software engineering (cs.SE). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CR, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.SE.
